																		Reeeepost
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/billith" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3042342); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3042342&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610204186" alt="Billith" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3042342)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/billith" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3042342); return false;" >Billith</a></span> <span class="odate time_1566520708 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">23 Aug 2019 00:38</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4337909">
									

<p>Sorry everyone but it deserves a fresh shot at life, no 001 should be under +100</p>
<p>This rewrite should allow it to stand on its own, regardless of the tale situation. But I just need to tweak some things on those and we'll be golden too :)</p>
<p>There should be enough hints and implications to figure out what's happening on a larger scale.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">spoiler</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Netzach&nbsp;means&nbsp;Eternity</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li>There are multiple real-life events and mythologies this corresponds to - GRB 060614, Great Oxygenation (timeline is a little fudged but who was around then to confirm it anyways), Sumerian mythos, etc</li>
<li>The cryo-chamber contains who the New Earth Foundation would call The Founder, but they aren't the Founder. The true founder had something else in mind when they started the Foundation</li>
<li>The notes at the end indicate everything was orchestrated by the Foundation, but this part of the Foundation has transcended to the point where their intentions are no longer discernable. The Foundation is a pluripotent god-organization.</li>
<li>The Foundation studied and used anomalies instead of fearing them and containing them from the world. There is no masquerade on Earth Prime. This is explained in more detail in <a href="/richard-larenz-personal-log">Richard Larenz Personal Log</a> and <a href="/a-place-to-call-your-home">A Place to Call Your Home</a></li>
<li>Netzach is the 7th sefirot (the same that brings yesod, keter, etc)- 7th sefirot - 7 gods of Sumerian mythos - Literally means &quot;eternity&quot; - 50 immortal children - etc etc</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Earth#/media/File:Earth_Western_Hemisphere.jpg">Earth Pic</a> compliant under public domain</p>
<p><a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/jamiec2009/5216377774/in/photolist-8WXinQ-3jdbAo-7ZdpBi-7pyhpD-7Zdki2-4pyAf1-mLLpsU-4VV4F9-7hccKz-7ZgBCb-7hcct8-7hg9Vh-7hgarm-dYwHQz-qYfepV-kuQfuD-4VV4G3-52kdMC-7hccze-65T9HR-eRGk6n-eE7awE-7hcch6-9rgqu-4VQZ28-hzGLWR-JXVCtf-eRUfPo-eRUPRS-7hg9Pf-etebx8-K1UZpr-4VQZ2c-eRUSCy-etgsE5-7hgakf-5dGjBb-phDuFx-8JdF27-eRdn1Y-eRGcS8-">probey boi</a> compliant under CC-BY, thanks Jamie C.</p>
<p>I'll come up with a compliant pic for the 3rd one, mark my words</p>
</div>
