<p>I appreciate the feedback, honestly I would rather have this than nothing. I'll take a look at what I can do, although it would be hard to justify 100% comprehension of a billion year old alien language (when it was completely written and similar to English there was people complaining about that too so idk). Maybe I'll make the spoken language cognitohazards like the written language.</p>
